(firstQuint)Tissue Repair Device (VergenixTM STR) in Patients With Epicondylitis (Tennis Elbow).

 The VergenixTM STR device is an advanced Soft tissue repair device, made of lyophilized Type I rhCollagen and Calcium Chloride that will be mixed with autologous PRP prior to injection for the repair of non ruptured tendon injuries (Tendinopathy).

 Three (3) ml of the mixed solution will be injected into the common extensor tendon.

